---
title: Sarh — Property submission, review, and deed issuance
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Citizen
    actor O as Registry officer
    participant W as apps/web (Angular)
    participant API as .NET 8 API
    participant DB as SQL Server
    participant FS as Storage<br/>(local FS)
    participant PDF as PAdES signer
    participant SSI as ACA-Py<br/>(Hyperledger Aries)
    actor V as Public verifier

    rect rgb(239, 246, 255)
    Note over C,DB: 1) Submission
    C->>W: fill form + draw polygon
    W->>API: POST /api/v1/properties { polygon, area, docs }
    API->>DB: INSERT properties (status='pending')
    API->>DB: INSERT registration_requests
    DB-->>API: property_id, request_no
    API-->>W: 201 SubmitResult
    end

    rect rgb(254, 252, 232)
    Note over O,DB: 2) Review
    O->>W: open /app/queue
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/properties?status=pending
    API->>DB: SELECT
    DB-->>W: list
    O->>W: open detail, read docs, view map
    O->>W: click "Approve" + decree no
    W->>API: POST /api/v1/properties/:id/review { decision: 'approve', approval_decree_no }
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET status='approved',<br/>reviewed_by_officer_id, approval_decree_no
    DB->>DB: AFTER UPDATE trigger → audit_log INSERT
    end

    rect rgb(236, 253, 245)
    Note over API,SSI: 3) Deed + VC issuance
    API->>PDF: generate deed PDF<br/>(citizen, polygon, decree)
    PDF-->>API: signed PAdES bytes + SHA256
    API->>FS: write deeds/<id>.pdf
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET deed_pdf_path, deed_signed_hash
    API->>SSI: issue VC (PropertyDeed) for citizen DID
    SSI-->>API: credential_id
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET vc_credential_id
    API->>DB: INSERT notifications (citizen, "deed ready")
    end

    rect rgb(254, 226, 226)
    Note over C,V: 4) Delivery + public verify
    C->>W: open /app/my/properties → download PDF
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/storage/deeds/<id>.pdf
    API->>FS: read file
    FS-->>C: PDF (with QR pointing to /verify/<code>)

    V->>W: scan QR / open /verify/<code>
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/verify/:code
    API->>DB: SELECT property + verify hash
    API-->>V: 200 { owner, area, decree, signed: true }
    end
